12:42.327 --> 12:45.424
The bathing costume
carriage wash was a smash hit!

12:45.491 --> 12:48.688
So now the NAGS are letting us
bring our act to Congress.

12:48.755 --> 12:50.520
Oh, I'm so excited!

12:50.588 --> 12:53.518
Lillian, this is our moment.

12:53.587 --> 12:55.251
I wish Hortense were alive

12:55.319 --> 12:57.016
so she could see us steal her dream.

12:57.086 --> 12:58.751
She's so selfish.

12:58.818 --> 13:00.683
Ladies, we came to wish you luck.

13:00.750 --> 13:02.347
Now get out there and tell the world

13:02.415 --> 13:04.246
that women deserve the right to vote.

13:04.313 --> 13:07.243
[LAUGHING]

13:07.313 --> 13:08.510
Sorry.

13:08.578 --> 13:10.243
Sorry, I thought you said "vote."

13:10.310 --> 13:12.241
[LAUGHTER CONTINUES]

13:12.310 --> 13:14.074
- We did.
- There's no time for joking.

13:14.143 --> 13:15.740
- We're at Congress.
- I've never joked

13:15.807 --> 13:17.005
in my entire life.

13:17.073 --> 13:18.404
This is why we're here?

13:18.472 --> 13:19.736
To help women get the right to vote?

13:19.805 --> 13:21.336
- Us?
- Why did you think

13:21.405 --> 13:22.535
- you were here?
- Oh, well, I figured

13:22.605 --> 13:24.203
it was an appearance.

13:24.270 --> 13:26.034
A sort of a meet and greet
for all of our new fans.

13:26.101 --> 13:28.365
No, it's about suffrage.

13:28.433 --> 13:30.031
That's why Hortense was famous.

13:30.101 --> 13:32.198
She was going to get us
the right to vote.

13:32.265 --> 13:33.597
You didn't know that?

13:33.663 --> 13:36.827
- No.
- I [Bleep] hate women!

13:37.895 --> 13:40.926
<i>[HIP-HOP MUSIC]</i>

13:48.722 --> 13:51.653
