that you stop taking advantage

14:44.290 --> 14:46.621
of Lady Dodo's kind heart
and generosity.

14:46.689 --> 14:50.319
- Or what?
- Or feel the full wrath

14:50.387 --> 14:51.819
of Mr. Peepers.

14:51.885 --> 14:53.650
All right, Mr. Peepers.

14:53.718 --> 14:55.251
Let me feel this wrath.

14:55.318 --> 14:57.347
