19:21.632 --> 19:23.563
Time for bed.

19:23.630 --> 19:25.395
Darling, never interrupt a man

19:25.465 --> 19:27.330
in the midst of his creative flow.

19:27.394 --> 19:29.225
But darling,
we haven't had carnal relations

19:29.294 --> 19:30.993
- since you've been here.
- I don't want anything

19:31.061 --> 19:32.724
