19:32.793 --> 19:35.558
You're not holding up
your end of the bargain.

19:35.625 --> 19:36.655
Which is?

19:36.725 --> 19:38.488
To [Bleep] me.

19:38.555 --> 19:40.486
Spending my money and mistreating me

19:40.555 --> 19:42.386
