20:05.073 --> 20:08.005
So I can go back to not owning my house

20:08.073 --> 20:10.836
and not having my own money?

20:10.903 --> 20:11.934
Yes.

20:12.003 --> 20:13.502
Get out!

20:13.571 --> 20:16.000
- Of the room?
- Get out of my house!

20:16.069 --> 20:17.601
All right.

20:17.667 --> 20:19.265
- I'm leaving then.
- Get out!

20:21.198 --> 20:22.462
