20:22.532 --> 20:24.463
I know you took it from my dresser.

20:24.530 --> 20:25.527
I was going to get another one.

20:25.596 --> 20:27.061
This is temporary.

20:29.526 --> 20:31.290
All I want in this world

20:31.360 --> 20:33.890
